    Inter Quartile Ranges

    iqrs.Rd

    Computes the IQR magnitude of a vector

    Usage

    iqrs(x, na.rm = FALSE)

    Arguments

    x

    A vector of values

    na.rm

    Logical. If `TRUE`, any `NA` and `NaN`'s are removed from `x` before the median and quantiles are computed.

    Examples

    iqrs(stats::rchisq(100, 2))
